name: agdelte-payments
include: .
depend:
  standard-library
-- Payment-provider clients (domain-agnostic). Currently the ЮKassa REST client
-- (Agdelte.Payment.YooKassa); Stripe (Agdelte.Payment.Stripe) and a future
-- provider-neutral interface can join here. Depends ONLY on the standard library
-- (outbound HTTP is its own http-client FFI; no framework HTTP server needed).
